      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Shine</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Watching everything turn around me </l>
          <l>While I'm standing in the place I've always been </l>
          <l>Seems like all these streets run behind me </l>
          <l>And I'm trying to find a way to get back in </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>Follow you... </l>
          <l>Slow... </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>As these days go by I'll be waiting </l>
          <l>While you find your way through places you don't know </l>
          <l>I'll be standing here never changing </l>
          <l>Only trying to be the place that you call home </l>
          <l>(Call home...) </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>I would follow you anywhere you go </l>
          <l>I would run with you however fast or slow </l>
          <l>I would make my way through this dark design </l>
          <l>I would run with you and everything (shine) </l>
          <l>And everything...</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
